Photo by FOLLOW & SHARE on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'wanna do the 2/2/2 rule On our wedding night, I told my wife that we now had a 2/2/2 rule. We got married in August and people still ask how long our honeymoon phase will last. I think it'll last as long as we stick to our 2's.'.
